%li[bill]
  != link_to(bill.bill_number, bill_path(bill.session, bill)) + " "
  != bill.title

  Status:
  = bill.actions.first.kind
  
  - if bill.votesmart_key_vote?
    This is a Votesmart Key Vote!

  .introduced
    Introduced:
    != bill.actions.minimum(:date)

  .recent_action
    Most recent action:
    != bill.actions.maximum(:date)
    
  .recent_vote
    != bill.votes.count
    votes have occurred on this bill